This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with improving the performance of the Transformer model for speech recognition tasks. Other likely sub-categories include cs.SD (Sound), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
